# Code owners for security-sensitive areas. Combined with a branch-protection
# rule that requires review from code owners, these paths cannot merge without
# an explicit human approval — see .github/workflows/pr-auto-merge.yml, which
# also refuses to auto-merge any PR that touches them.
#
# NOTE: enforcement of "review required" still needs a branch-protection rule on
# `main` (Settings → Branches) with "Require review from Code Owners" enabled.
# The workflow gate is the in-repo half of the control.

